assets.name: assets/9Rk_g-pp3jw
assets.description:
Clipped from the model by Jost Hobic

Bodmin mmor is fantastic landscape. Here on 3D model we can see area around Rough Tor.

We can see nicel preserved landscape of Bronze Age villiages and monumental stone cairn (Neolithic) that runs towards peak of Rough Tor.

More here https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bodmin_Moor Time Team episode https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-dROrgcniWk

Data used https://catalogue.ceh.ac.uk/documents/e2a742df-3772-481a-97d6-0de5133f4812

License:
CC Attribution

Original model at https://sketchfab.com/3d-models/bodmin-moor-687efc70cca143b2a946177444f2f974
